    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "really? i always thought that's a core part of the argument for it—that it builds a 'bottom-up' economy. are you saying the whole thing is basically just a failed economic theory then? like, is there any actual economic benefit to it at all, or is it just about making people feel better?",
